    <summary>An extension implementing the Sailthru API.</summary>
    <description>This extension does the following:&#xD;
      -Overrides all emails sent through Magento to be sent through Sailthru, allowing records of the emails to be kept.&#xD;
      -Maintains carts and sends abandoned cart emails, improving your rate of sale.&#xD;
      -Records all orders submitted.&#xD;
      -Adds all registered users along with their info to an email list, for easy and custom eBlasts.&#xD;
      -Adds subscribers to a separate list for simple newsletters.</description>
    <notes>First version. Send suggestions at https://www.sailthru.com/contact</notes>
